Dialogs.Dialog: Today's Rinko's birthday... I'm sure you know.
Happy Birthday Rinko！ Come on, say it, will you？
Rinko's birthday... Did you remember it？ Hehe.
Today's the day. Umm... for my birthday.
Happy Birthday！ Do you want me to celebrate？ It can't be helped.
Happy Birthday. You and Rinko should celebrate together.
You know, today's the day we met for the first time. Did you know that？
Today is the anniversary of your first meeting with Rinko. Hehe.
Today is the day when you and Rinko met for the first time. Remember that.
Do you remember the day when you and Rinko started dating？ Today's is the anniversary of that day.
You know, today is the anniversary of when you and Rinko started dating. Should we celebrate？
Today is the anniversary of the day we started dating. Rinko remembers it well♪
Monday has arrived... it's the start of the week.
It's still Tuesday. What shall we do today？
Wednesday. I'm not getting into it...
It's finally Thursday. Should we think about plans for the weekend？
Here it is, Friday. I've worked hard all week！
On Saturdays, you just want to think about fun, don't you？ Of course, tomorrow too.
Come on, it's Sunday, play hard and relieve stress！
Spring is dawning... can't get up that early, though.
It's so hot... I want to write "aestivation", and be able to sleep in the summer.
Autumn, huh... it's nice to be pensive once in a while, isn't it？
Too cold... Rinko curls up in a kotatsu.
What is it？ If you need something, be brief. If you don't, turn around.
Somehow... I thought you would come.
You're finally here. You made me wait too long.
Ah, here they come. I almost got tired of waiting.
I've been waiting for you. If I can't meet you... I'll be bored.
You should come earlier... I felt lonely.
Over here. Are you happy to see Rinko's face？
You're here today too？ Of course I'm happy.
You're late！ I've been waiting for you for a long time... Hehe.
I smiled when I saw your face.
Could you come see me a lot more？
It's frustrating, but... I want to see you a lot more.
I though it was about time you arrived.
Rinko wants to see you. A lot more ofter if possible.
Come on, we'll go out a lot, don't we？
Here you are... Not that I've been waiting for you.
Hehe... can you tell me how much you missed Rinko？
Happy New Year. Wishing for your and Rinko's happiness, are you going to the First Shrine visit of the year？
It was one Fuji, two hawks, and three boyfriends... Is it good luck？ Hehe.
Tell me your first dream of the year. Don't tell me there's no Rinko in it？
Did you have your first dream？ Rinko's first dream had you in it, just as I thought.
Today is February 14... I can't help it, let's get ready, shall we？
If you get chocolate from someone other than Rinko, it'll be confiscated.
Rinko may not be in character, but... look forward to it today♪
Let's see, today is White Day... Hmm？ Just talking to myself.
Today is White Day, huh... Sounds pretty good, doesn't it？
Today is White Day, so will you do whatever Rinko says？
Lying is the beginning of thievery... is that true？
You seem to be a terrible liar, don't you？
How about a reverse April Fool's Day？ You absolutely can't lie for a day.
Speaking of field trips？ Potato chips, of course. It's common sense.
A choir competition, huh. Come on, go for it！
It's Tanabata today. Since it's so special, why don't you write your wishes on tanzaku strips？
It's the Towano Festival. Will there lots of food stalls？
Sports festival... who thought about that？ It's a hassle.
Can Rinko get some Halloween candy？ For now, trick or treat！
A cultural festival, huh. Well, it's fun in its own way, isn't it？ Hehe.
Umm... do you really want to spend Christmas Eve with Rinko？
Christmas Eve？ I don't really mind... if we stay together.
It's already here... Eve is here♪
New Year's Eve is the one day of the year when you can stay up late and no one will get mad♪
Today is the day the exam results are announced. Well, I guess it's too late to worry about it now.
Hey, it's Rinko's birthday soon. Of course, I'm sure you know that.
Speaking of which, is it about time？ Here's your...
When did you and Rinko start dating？ Ah... it's coming soon. Hehe.
Chocolate is everywhere this time of year, isn't it？ Are you expecting it？
It's almost White Day. By the way, why is it white？
April Fool's Day is coming soon. Don't worry, Rinko won't lie. Hehe.
We have a field trip coming up, right？ It's such a hassle, but we'll have potato chips as a snack.
A choir competition, huh... Well, what happens now？
It's almost Tanabata, and summer is finally here. Summer vacation is coming soon.
The Towano Festival is just around the corner. Well, I guess I can go with you.
Ah, the dreaded day is approaching. Why is there such a thing as a sports festival？
I found a Halloween pumpkin today. It's that of the year already.
It's almost time for the cultural festival but, can you get me motivated？
Christmas is just around the corner. Not that I'm in high spirits, though.
The year is almost over. A lot has happened, but I guess it was a satisfying year, right？
There will be a test soon, huh... Well, it's fine.
Can I expect tomorrow？ Tomorrow we'll have lots of fun.
Tomorrow is, umm... No, it's nothing.
Remember our date today？ If you forget it, you'll get a small kick！
Hey！ It's time for our date. Hurry up, hurry up！
Just don't be late for tomorrow's date, okay？
Do you have something you want to eat？ ...I'm just asking.
Just like this city is developing, do you think your relationship with Rinko will develop as well？
Hey, I heard there's a new shop. Do you want to try it？
Do you know what spots are popular these days？ Keep an eye out for it.
Hey, why haven't you emailed me lately？
You know, I haven't been getting a lot of emails lately... Not that I care.
You haven't emailed me lately... Rinko feels lonely...
You and Rinko haven't seen each other lately, have we？ Are you going to stay like this？
Hey, why haven't we seen each other lately？ Are you just going to leave Rinko like this？
You haven't seen me at all lately... Don't you know how Rinko feels？
You know... we haven't been kissing much lately... have we？
You know... we haven't been kissing much lately. Why？
Lately, umm... we haven't kissed as much, have we？ Are you sick of it？
You don't look well... Even though I act like this, Rinko... is worried about you.
You study seems to be going okay. Good, good.
Don't tell me you're studying behind Rinko's back？ You're doing great.
How's your body feeling？ Well, keep up the good work.
Your body is in great shape！
You seem to be looking good lately. That's good.
What is that？ I feel a great sense of style！
Maybe you're looking kinda cool these days... I'm a little nervous.
Somehow these days you are... you know, cool.
Well, think of it as a little late Valentine's Day present.
It would be a waste not to get a return gift on White Day.
